  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the prevalence of characteristics of pain in a
      cohort of patients with prior stroke suspected of having central post stroke pain, identified
      through a postal questionnaire.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Medical history, pain history, pain drawing, DN4, sensory examination.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
